Inexperienced Class A Drivers

Drive for RGM Family

RECENT DRIVING SCHOOL GRADUATE OR LIMITED CLASS A EXPERIENCE? No problem.

RGM Family offers an orientation and flatbed training program just for you! We've been training apprentice drivers for nearly 30 years.

Apprentice Training Program

Our student driver (apprentice) training program is recognized as one of the best in the country. Our program is one of the few on-the-job truck driver training programs approved by the Department of Labor as a certified Heavy Truck Driver Apprenticeship program.

If you are already enrolled in a CDL training program or have limited experience:

  • Call us at 800.247.2862 for more information
  • Obtain an RGM Family application from your school, fill it out, and have them send it to us
  • Complete our apprentice driver application

Orientation & Training

Orientation is two weeks at one of our training facilities located in Des Moines, Iowa or Columbia, South Carolina. Orientation is followed by five weeks over-the-road (OTR) with a Driver Trainer. Home time is important, so we try to pair you with a trainer within 150 miles of your home.

Your first 7 days (Mon-Sun) is classroom instruction and hands-on load securement training. Remaining 5 days (Mon-Fri) are equipment familiarization before going OTR with a Driver Trainer.

Apprentice drivers are paid $650 per week during orientation and OTR training. Please contact a recruiter for more details.

Why RGM Family?

  • Weekend Home Time
  • Industry-Leading Pay (Some first-year drivers earn $100,000+/year)
  • Top Quality Peterbilt Equipment
  • Flatbed Training with Experts in Safety and Load Securement

Military Veterans

Visit our Veteran Page!

RGM FAMILY IS EMPLOYEE-OWNED

Don't just settle for another job. Very few companies in the U.S. are Employee-Owned. RGM Family is proud to be one of those few.

Orientation Facilities

RGM Family Training Facility - Columbia, South Carolina
